settings.description:
Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.   

To carry Flurries, check out the Flurry Carrying level. You'll solve the first puzzle much quicker.
Smaghetti is really not functioning properly, everything was working fine one day, and then the other it starts glitching out. Just ignore the graphical issues. I hope this gets patched.
This is a Level Remaked From Super Mario World, Awesome Level Dude!
Magic Blocks, are on Buster Beetle Room, also Room 4 is Bonus Room, so Enjoy!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!

Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.    

Hint: You can carry Flurries when above and on the side of it.
Bullet Bills and Goombas' with shoes seem to want to ruin your day as you compete in the Green Mountain Climbing Contest.
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.
